column5: Just wondering if anyone has any info on the fishing at Lake Ogascanan in Quebec?

Wizard:There's a wealth of information on this board about Lake Ogascanan in Quebec. But rather than try to repeat much of it, it's much easier to suggest you use the search function - search for Ogascanan. I did this (checked off search archives) and there were over two pages of references to previous posts.
Fished there 2 years ago. What information do you need?
